column1: Dɛn ne Euler tour traversal a ɛfa tree bi ho?
column2: Nantew a wɔde twa tree no ho hyia, a wofi ase fi ntini no so, baabi a wohu node biara mprɛnsa: efi benkum, fi ase, fi nifa.
column3: ɛhyɛ node ase wɔ ntini no benkum so na afei ɛkɔ node biara hɔ wɔ benkum kosi nifa nhyehyɛe mu, kɔ ntini no hɔ, na afei ɛkɔ so san di saa dwuma no bio wɔ tree no nifa so.

column1: Nsɛdi bɛn na ɛwɔ iteration ne recursion ntam?
column2: Wɔn baanu nyinaa fa nsɛm a wɔka no mpɛn pii ho; wɔn baanu nyinaa wɔ sɔhwɛ ahorow a wɔde gyae dwumadi no; abien no nyinaa betumi aba a ano nsi da.
column3: wɔn baanu nyinaa tumi yɛ nnwuma a wɔtaa yɛ mpɛn pii. nanso recurisve gyina nneɛma ahorow soronko bi so na ɛkyerɛkyerɛ ne exit clause a yenim  sɛ ebedu ho. Iterative ka loop a ɛsan yɛ mpɛn dodow a wɔadi kan ahyɛ, anaasɛ ɛhwɛ sɛ ebia exit clause bi wɔ hɔ bere biara mu.

column1: Wobɛyɛ dɛn atumi de stack a ɛwɔ nnidiso su adi dwuma?
column2: Ma stack no atifi nkyerɛ nkitahodi nhyehyɛe no ti, enti push ne pop dwumadi no de nneɛma ahorow bɛka ho anaa ɛbɛyi afiri hɔ wɔ nhyehyɛe no mfitiase.
column3: W'ankasa no wo gya kwan bere a stack no nyin no. Stack no betumi ayɛ tenten sɛnea wuhia.

column1: Nneɛma bɛn na ɛwɔ software mu a sɔhwɛ fa no nya so nkɛntɛnso?
column2: Sɔhwɛ fa no betumi anya coding stage (ɔfa 5) ne solution refinement stage ((ɔfa 7) nyinaa so nkɛntɛnso .
column3: Sɛ design no sɔhwɛ fa no da ɔhaw ahorow adi a... Sɛ nhyehyɛe no ntumi nyɛ adwuma wɔ ne mprempren tebea mu a ɛbɛma wɔanya bere a wɔde yɛ adwuma akyiri yi kyɛn sɛnea wɔbuu akontaa mfiase no a, ebetumi aka nneɛma a wɔyɛ no. Afei nso ɛka coding efisɛ sɛ wosɔ hwɛ wie a ebia ɛho behia sɛ wosan kyerɛw ahyɛnsode anaa code no ma program no de yi mfomso ahorow fi hɔ.

column1: Nsonsonoe bɛn na ɛda data member ne local nsakrae a ɛwɔ member dwumadi mu ntam?
column2: Wobetumi anya data member ahorow afi member dwumadie biara a ɛwɔ adesua nkyerɛase no mu. Local nsakrae no betumi akɔ mu nkutoo wɔ member dwumadi a ɛkyerɛkyerɛ mu no mu.
column3: Wontumi mfa mpɔtam hɔ nsakrae ahorow nni dwuma. Sɛ dwumadi bi ba awiei a, nsakrae ahorow a ɛde ba no nso yera. Faako a sɛ data member ahorow yɛ nsakrae wɔ nkyerɛase mu no, na saa ade no wɔ hɔ afebɔɔ.

column1: Dɛn ne ntonto anaa queue?
column2: Data nhyehyɛe a etumi kora nneɛma ahorow, a ɛwɔ su sɛ ade a etwa tow a wɔde bɛka ho no bɛyɛ nea etwa tow a wɔbeyi afiri hɔ (anaasɛ nea edi kan-a ɛkɔ mu-nea edi kan-a epue).
column3: Ntonto anaa queue kora nneɛma anaa element ahorow bi wɔ nhyehyɛe pɔtee bi mu. Ne nnyinasosɛm a ɛfa operahyin ho ne FIFO(first in first out-nea edi kan a ɛkɔ mu, nea edi kan a ɛpue), a ɛkyerɛ sɛ element a edi kan a wɔde hyɛ mu no ne nea edi kan a woyi fi hɔ.

column3: Queue anaa ntonto te sɛ array, gye sɛ wobetumi anya data no nnidiso nnidiso nkutoo. Nea ɛnte sɛ stack no, queue di FIFO akyi…(First in, First out) Nea edi kan wɔ mu, Nea edi kan fi mu.

column1: Kyerɛkyerɛ tiawa wɔ kasamu biako mu sɛnea nhyehyɛe a ɛbom anaa merge sort yɛ adwuma?

column3: Merge sort fa array bi na ɛkyekyɛ mu abien na ɛde fa biara san kɔ ne ho na ɛka bom na ɛhyehyɛ fa abien no bere a ɛfiri ase san kɔ soro.

column1: Dɛn ne tree a ɛyɛ abien?
column2: Tree a mma anaa nkorabata dodow a ɛwɔ soro kɛse biara wɔ node biara mu yɛ abien.
column3: Nodes a ɛyɛ hwee anaa nea ɛboro saa, a wɔakyekyɛ mu ayɛ no ntini node ne set abien a ebia ɛda mpan a ɛyɛ tree abien. Enti, anyɛ yiye koraa no, node biara a ɛwɔ tree a ɛwɔ abien mu no wɔ mma anaa nkorabata baanu, benkum ne nifa.

column1: Dɛn ne ɔhaw titiriw a ɛwɔ nhyehyɛe a ɛwɔ nkitahodi abien so kyɛn mfitiase nkitahodi nhyehyɛe?
column2: Akwan foforo ho hia  a wɔde bɛkora akyi pointer ahorow no.
column3: Node biara hwehwɛ sɛ wonya pointer foforo, na egye kwan pii. insertions ne deletions hwehwɛ sɛ wɔyɛ pointer dwumadie pii.

column1: Dɛn ne ahaban anaa leaf?

column1: Dɛn ne nhyehyɛe a ɛwɔ nkitahodi?
column2: Nneɛma a wɔaboaboa ano a wobetumi asesa mu.
column3: Nhyehyɛe nkitahodi yɛ nhyehyɛe a ɛwɔ structs anaa records a wɔfrɛ no nodes. Anyɛ yiye koraa no, node biara wɔ members abien, na emu biako twe adwene si ade anaa node a edi hɔ a ɛwɔ list no mu so.

column1: Wobɛyɛ dɛn ayi node bi afi search tree abien mu?
column2: Hwehwɛ node no, afei fa benkum so node a efi ne nifa subtree (anaasɛ nifa so node a efi ne benkum subtree) si ananmu.
column3: Wode recursion hwehwɛ tree no mu ma node no. Sɛ wuhu node no a, wubehu sɛ ɛyɛ ahaban anaasɛ node a ɛwɔ mu. Sɛ ɛyɛ leaf anaa ahaban a, wobɛyi  kɛkɛ na wode parent pointer a ɛwɔ saa node no so no ahyɛ NULL. Sɛ ɛyɛ node a, wode node mma anaa nkorabata no mu biara besi node no ananmu.

column1: Dɛn ne inorder traversal a ɛwɔ tree abien?
column2: Fa benkum so tree ketewa no, afei ntini no, afei nifa so tree ketewa no.
column3: Hyɛ ase fi ntini no so wɔ nnidiso kwan so, afei yɛ nifa ne benkum

column1: Ɔkwan bɛn so na dwumadi ahorow  a ɛboro so no da nsow wɔ nea ɛboaboa ano anaa compiler no mu?
column2: Egyina dwumadi ahyɛnsode so . Sɛ dwumadi no boro so a, compiler no bɛhunu dwumadi a n'ahyɛnsode bɛn ɔfrɛ dwumadi no.
column3: Compiler paw dwumadi a ɛfata sɛ ɔbɛyɛ a egyina nɔma, ahorow ne nhyehyɛe a ɛwɔ akyinnyegye anaa anobaebae mu wɔ dwumadi frɛ no mu.

column1: Nsonsonoe bɛn na ɛda dwumadie nhwɛsoɔ ne dwumadie nkyerɛaseɛ ntam?
column2: Dwumadi nhwɛso bi ka dwumadi ahyɛnsode, kyerɛ sɛ, dwumadi no din, sanba su, ne nneɛma a egyina so no su. Dwumadie nkyerɛase no ka dwumadi no adeban ankasa ho.
column3: Dwumadi nhyehyɛe yɛ paemuka kɛkɛ a ɛkyerɛ dwumadi bi a ɛwɔ hɔ, na yentumi mfa nni dwuma sɛ dwumadi ankasa. Ɛsɛ sɛ wɔyɛ dwumadi bi a nkyerɛase bi wɔ mu na ama wɔaka nea dwumadi no yɛ akyerɛ nea ɔboaboa ano no.

column1: Nsonsonoe bɛn na ɛda data member ne local nsakrae a ɛwɔ member dwumadi mu ntam?
column2: Wobetumi anya data member ahorow afi member dwumadie biara a ɛwɔ adesua nkyerɛase no mu. Local nsakrae no betumi akɔ mu nkutoo wɔ member dwumadi a ɛkyerɛkyerɛ mu no mu.
column3: Data member no yɛ nea dwumadi nyinaa tumi kɔ mu wɔ ekuw no mu, baabi a local nsakrae no wɔ hɔ ma member dwumadi no nko ara na ɛyera bere a yɛagyae dwumadi no.

column1: Mfaso titiriw bɛn na ɛwɔ nhyehyɛe a ɛwɔ nkitahodi abien so kyɛn nhyehyɛe a ɛwɔ nkitahodi titiriw?
column2: Wobetumi ayɛ deletion (yi firi mu) ne insertion (fa hyɛ mu) dwumadie nyinaa wɔ bere ano bere ano, a saa dwumadie a wɔyɛ ansa na beae bi a wɔde ama wɔ nhyhyɛe no mu anaa wɔ nhyhyɛe no awiee no ka ho.
column3: Wubetumi atwa nhyehyɛe no mu akɔ w’anim ne akyi nyinaa.

column1: Dɛn ne ntonto anaa queue?
column2: Data nhyehyɛe a ɛkora element ahorow anaa nneɛma ahorow a ɛde nea edi kan kɔ mu, nea edi kan pue nhyehyɛe di dwuma. Operehyin no a ɛwɔ ntonto anaa queue no mu ne enqueue ɛnna dequeue.
column3: Te sɛ nkitahodi nhyehyɛe gye sɛ ɛyɛ nea edi kan wɔ nea etwa tow a epue (first in and last out)

column1: Nsonsonoe bɛn na ɛda data member ne local nsakrae a ɛwɔ member dwumadi mu ntam?

column1: Nsonsonoe bɛn na ɛda dwumadi nhwɛso ne dwumadie nkyerɛaseɛ ntam?

column3: FUNCTION PROTOTYPE no ne baabi a programmer no pae mu ka sɛ ɔde dwumadi a ɛnyɛ titiriw anaa ankasa( ) redi dwuma. Eyi te sɛ nea wɔrebɔ nsesae bi ho dawuru, programmer no nim sɛ ɔde bedi dwuma daakye, nanso onnya nkaa baabi a wɔde bedi dwuma, anaa ɔkwan a wɔbɛfa so de adi dwuma. Eyi  bua asɛmmisa a ɛne sɛ hena, ɛma dwumadi no din ne suban. Dwumadi nhwɛso no, ɛnam adeyɛ a wɔtaa yɛ so no, wɔde si dwumadi no mfitiase....akyi ne ansa na titiriw no( ). ADWUMA NKYERƐKYERƐMU no yɛ adwuma no biribiara. Eyi ne baabi a programmer no si nea dwumadi no bɛyɛ ho gyinae na ɔka sɛnea ɔbɛyɛ no kyerɛ no. Egye nsɛm biara a wɔde ma no na ɛyɛ oprehyɛn ahorow no. Ɛyɛ adwuma te sɛ adwene no, adwene no gye nsɛm a wɔde ba mu na egyina saa nsɛm no so yɛ adwuma wɔ ɔkwan bi so de nsɛm bi ba. Wɔde dwumadi nkyerɛase no ato titiriw no( ) ne dwumadi foforo biara akyi. Dwumadi yɛ n’ankasa ade na ɛsɛ sɛ wosusuw ho sɛ ɛte saa.

column3: Coding ne Debugging program ahorow no taa yɛ mmerɛw, efisɛ compiler no bɛkyerɛ ade a ɛreyɛ adwuma wɔ ɔkwan a ɛnteɛ so, anaasɛ adwuma a wɔde ama ade bi no bɛyɛ mmerɛw sɛ wobehu. Code no ankasa nso hwɛ sɛ wɔahyehyɛ no yiye na ɛnyɛ den sɛ wɔbɛkenkan na ɛbɛboa ma wɔakwati coding a ɛho nhia. Dwumadi no akyi nsiesie nso yɛ mmerɛw. Afei nso, wobetumi asan de module ahorow adi dwuma mpɛn pii wɔ nhyehyɛe afoforo mu a ɛnyɛ ɔhaw pii. Abstraction anaa wɔayi biribi afiri hɔ yɛ adwinni a wɔde kyekyɛ ɔhaw kɛse biako mu yɛ no ɔhaw nketenkete a ɛnyɛ den na wodi ho dwuma. Wɔkyɛ ɔhaw nketewa no pii wɔ ɔhaw soronko a ɛyɛ den ntam, na sɛ wobɔ module ahorow a wode bedi eyinom ho dwuma de adi ɔhaw nketewa a wɔsan yɛ no ho dwuma a, ebetumi akora bere so bere a wuhyia bio no.

Ɛma kwan ma wotumi fi benkum, nifa ne ase kɔsra node biara. Euler akwantuo no di kan kɔ n’anim kɔ benkum so abofra sɛ bi wɔ hɔ a, afei ɛkɔ n’awofo so, afei ɛyɛ abofra a odi hɔ, afei ɛyɛ ɔwofo awofo.

Arrays wɔ random access na overheads sua sɛ wɔde toto Linked list ho a, ɛwɔ sequential access nkutoo a overheads dɔɔso dodo na enni cache memory support. column1: Dwuma bɛn na header-file di?
column2: Sɛ wobɛkora class interface a, data member ahorow ne member dwumadi nhyehyɛe ka ho
column3: Fael a ɛwɔ ti no yɛ "reusable" source code te sɛ class a ɛwɔ fael a sɛnea wɔtaa yɛ no wɔ .h fael din ntrɛwmu. Eyi yɛ soronko wɔ .cpp fael a "source-code" wom ho.

column1: Kyerɛkyerɛ tiawa wɔ kasamu biako mu sɛnea nhyehyɛe a wɔaka abom anaa merge sort yɛ adwuma?
column2: Ɛkyekyɛ mfitiase nhyehyɛe no mu abien, hyehyɛ fã abien no mu biara, na afei ɛka nhyehyɛe a wɔahyehyɛ no bom.
column3: Mergesort kyekyɛ nhyehyɛe no mu yɛ no fã nketewa na afei ɛka subarray ahorow a wɔahyehyɛ no bom yɛ no nhyehyɛe biako a wɔahyehyɛ.

column1: Dɛn ne dwumadi atitiriw a ɛbata stack ho?
column2: pia na pop
column3: Push, Pop, na ɔkyerɛwee

column1: Wobɛyɛ dɛn atumi de stack a ɛwɔ nhyehyɛe adi dwuma?
column2: Ma stack no atifi nkyerɛ nkitahodi nhyehyɛe no ti, enti pia ne pop dwumadi no de nneɛma ahorow bɛka ho anaa ɛbɛyi afiri hɔ wɔ nhyehyɛe no mfitiase.
column3: Nodes a wode bedi dwuma de ahwɛ stack no ti so. Afei fa Push( ) ne Pop ( ) yɛ stack no sɛnea ɛho hia.

column1: Nsonsonoe bɛn na ɛda dwumadi nhwɛso ne dwumadi nkyerɛase ntam?
column2: Dwumadi nhwɛso bi ka dwumadi ahyɛnsode, kyerɛ sɛ, dwumadi no din, sanba su, ne nneɛma a egyina so no su. Dwumadie nkyerɛase no ka dwumadi no adeban ankasa ho.
column3: function prototype kyerɛkyerɛ classes interface a enni reviling biribiara a ɛwɔ mu sɛnea ɛfa function nkyerɛase no ntumi nyɛ saa.

column1: Dɛn ne tree?
column2: Node ahorow a wɔaboaboa ano, a ɛwɔ node soronko bi a wɔfrɛ no root, ne node a aka no, wɔakyekyɛ mu akɔ kuw biako anaa nea ɛboro saa a enni twaka mu, kuw biara yɛ tree.
column3: Dua yɛ data nhyehyɛe a wɔde node ahorow bata wɔn ho wɔn ho ho wɔ ɔkwan a ɛyɛ nhyehyɛe so.

column1: Wobɛyɛ dɛn atumi de stack a ɛwɔ array adi dwuma?
column2: Ma stack no atifi nkɔ array no awiei, enti pia ne pop dwumadi no bɛka anaa ayi elements afiri array no nifa so.
column3: Fa pointer a ɛkyerɛ array list no awiei bere nyinaa ma push/pop nsakrae ahorow di dwuma.

column1: Dɛn ne wiase nyinaa nsakrae ahorow no kɛse?
column2: File no kɛse.
column3: wobetumi de C++ fael biara akɔ wɔn so wɔ baabiara.

column1: Dɛn na nsoromma (*) dwumadie no san de ba?
column2: Alias (nsɛmfua a ɛne ne ho di nsɛ) ma ade a etumi sesa wɔ memory mu no . Ɛyɛ operator a ɛde nsonsonee no ba.
column3: san de asɛmfua a ɛne ade a ne pointer operand no twe adwene si so no hyia.

column1: Ɔkwan bɛn so na wobetumi adi array bi ho dwuma wɔ pointer mu?
column2: Ɛdenam pointer a wobɛhyɛ aseɛde akyerɛ nneɛma a edi kan wɔ array no mu, na afei wode array element no ahyɛnsode  ahyɛ pointer yi akɔ soro.
column3: Element A[n] betumi akɔ so denam *(APtr + n) so.

column1: Dɛn ne sɔhwɛ kwan a wɔfa so susuw bere a nhyehyɛe bi rekɔ so?
column2: Fa nhyehyɛe no di dwuma na kari mmere a ɛde bedi dwuma.
column3: Nnyinasosɛm bi a wɔde kan di dwuma a ɛkyerɛ oprehyɛn dodow a wɔyɛ wɔ algorithm bi mu.

column1: Nsonsonoe titiriw bɛn na ɛda bere tiaa bi ne ayɛ ntam…bere a wode asɛm bi ato gua?
column2: Block a ɛwɔ mu no ayɛ...wɔ bere a nsɛm no bɛyɛ adwuma anyɛ yiye koraa no pɛnkoro.
column3: While loop a wɔde di dwuma de yɛ block of code bere tenten a tebea bi yɛ nokware. Do...while loop a wɔde yɛ block of code bere tenten a tebea bi di mu. Nsonsonoe a ɛda while ne do...while ntam ne sɛ while loop sɔ ne tebea hwɛ ansa na wɔayɛ ne mu nsɛm no na do...while loop no sɔ ne tebea hwɛ bere a wɔadi ne mu nsɛm no anyɛ yiye koraa no pɛnkoro.

column1: Nsonsonoe titiriw bɛn na ɛda strings a wɔde type string no abɔ ho dawuru ne strings a wɔde nkyerɛwde nhyehyɛe a wɔde abɔ ho dawuru no ntam?
column2: Nhama a wɔde nkyerɛwde nhyehyɛe a wɔde abɔ ho dawuru no wɔ element a hwee nni mu a wɔde aka ho wɔ nhyehyɛe no awiei.
column3: nkyerɛwde ahorow no wɔ tenten a wɔahyɛ, bere a ɛkame ayɛ sɛ type string no tenten nni anohyeto.

column1: Dɛn na wɔtaa de ka adesuakuw nkyerɛase ho?
column2: Data members (su ahorow) ne member dwumadi ahorow.
column3: Yɛn deɛ ɛtaa yɛ set, get, ne displayMessge anaa nkra foforɔ a ɛkyerɛ wo properties a class bi wɔ nanso ɛnda ne implementations adi. Wubetumi anya biribiara a wopɛ wɔ w’ankasa adesuakuw nkyerɛase mu.

column1: Ɔkwan bɛn so na wɔde arrays kɔ dwumadi so?
column2: denam nsɛm a wɔde gyina so so.
column3: Dwumadi no kenkan nsakrae ahorow no, sie. afei ɛsan de nea variable no kenkan biara no ba. Afei function no tintim array no mu nsɛm.

column1: Mfaso titiriw bɛn na ɛwɔ array ahorow so kyɛn nkitahodi nhyehyɛe ahorow no?
column2: Wobetumi akɔ element ahorow a ɛwɔ array mu no tee (a ɛne nkitahodi nhyehyɛe bɔ abira, a ɛhwehwɛ sɛ wɔsan twa mu bio).
column3: Linked list wɔ nkɔanim a ɛyɛ den wɔ dwumadie no mu. Linked list no wɔ array a ɛkɔ so nyin a ɛma memory kɔ soro.
